    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80f9-842a-e4cf5028dafe",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Over the years, feedback has evolved to be lerner-centered process, in the sense that feedback provided is useful for students to address future tasks. The study collects instructor feedback on 2-consecutive assignments from a data science course. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-80f9-842a-e4cf5028dafe",
        "parent": {
