      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-8052-b521-ed679380ea50",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors use changes in performance as a proxy of learning outcomes. Segmentation analysis is performed and the features extracted from the data were used to subsequently predict learning outcomes → with interpretation being provided by SHAP. Authors find that:",
